9 lieu thereof the phrase "prepare an entry in the department's records that is accessible to law
10 enforcement via MULES and"; and
11
12 Further amend said bill and section, Page 2, Line 22, by deleting the words "Such entry" and
13 inserting in lieu thereof the following:
14
15 " Such entry as related to the applicant’s driver’s license shall remain active until the expiration
16 of their driver’s license. Such entry as related to the applicant’s motor vehicle license plate or
17 plates"; and
18
19 Further amend said bill, page, and section, Line 24, by deleting the word "system" and inserting
20 in lieu thereof the word "records."; and
21
22 Further amend said bill by amending the title, enacting clause, and intersectional references
23 accordingly.
